            <title><![CDATA[Battlefield 6 finally has its Season One trailer, showing new weapons, maps, and a tactical game mode]]></title>
            <link>https://www.eurogamer.net/battlefield-6-finally-has-its-season-one-trailer-showing-new-weapons-maps-and-a-tactical-game-mode</link>
